		"_postman_id": "blog-management-api-2026",
		"name": "Blog Management Platform API",
		"description": "Complete API collection for Blog Management Platform with authentication, user management, and blog CRUD operations.\n\n**Author:** Dinusha Herath\n**Date:** February 7, 2026\n**Assignment:** Decryptogen Technical Assessment\n\n## Features:\n- JWT Authentication\n- Role-based access control (ADMIN/USER)\n- Blog CRUD operations\n- Auto-summarization\n- Pagination support\n\n## Usage:\n1. Register a user or login\n2. Copy the token from response\n3. Token is auto-saved to environment variable\n4. Protected endpoints automatically use the token\n\n## Environment Variables:\n- `base_url`: http://localhost:3000\n- `token`: Auto-set after login\n- `user_id`: Auto-set after registration/login\n- `blog_id`: Auto-set after creating a blog",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Authentication",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register User",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    const response = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (response.user && response.user.id) {",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"user_id\", response.user.id);",
									"        console.log(\"User ID saved:\", response.user.id);",
									"    }",
									"    pm.test(\"User registered successfully\", function() {",
									"        pm.expect(response.message).to.include(\"registered\");",
									"    });",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n    \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\",\n    \"role\": \"USER\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"auth",
								"register"
							]
						},
						"description": "Register a new user account.\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `name` (required): User's full name\n- `email` (required): Unique email address\n- `password` (required): Password (will be hashed)\n- `role` (optional): \"USER\" or \"ADMIN\" (default: \"USER\")\n\n**Response:**\n- 201: User created successfully\n- 400: Email already registered\n- 500: Server error"
					},
					"response": []
				},
