							"raw": "{{base_url}}/blogs",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"blogs"
							]
						},
						"description": "Create a new blog post (Authenticated users).\n\n**Headers:**\n- Authorization: Bearer {token}\n- Content-Type: application/json\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `title` (required): Blog title\n- `content` (required): Full blog content\n\n**Response:**\n- 201: Blog created (summary auto-generated)\n- 401: Unauthorized\n- 500: Server error\n\n**Note:** Summary is automatically generated from first 200 characters."
					},
					"response": []
				},
